# ğŸ“Š Sales Performance Analytics Dashboard

This project is a Sales Performance Analytics Dashboard developed using **Python, Streamlit, Pandas, and Matplotlib**. The goal of this project is to analyze sales trends, track revenue, and visualize business performance across regions and product categories.

The dashboard allows users to filter data interactively and monitor key performance indicators such as **total revenue, units sold, and average unit price**.

